==============================================================
====================Blobby Volley 2 README====================
=============The head-to-head multiplayer ball game===========
==============================================================
=================http://blobby.sourceforge.net================
==============================================================

System requirements:

Either Windows 95 or later, or Linux
Graphics card with DirectDraw-Acceleration (on Windows)
OpenGL-compliant graphics card recommended (both systems)

You can hire/buy banner ads of the new background (strand1.bmp).
Contact us per EMail: Daniel-Knobe@web.de

The "Dedicaded Server" runs with a Gamespeed of 125%.

Source code:

On Linux, with Subversion installed just type:
 svn co https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/blobby blobby

For further instructions see
http://sourceforge.net/svn/?group_id=169341

